OL,6,FA woman from is being sent to Ukraine
OL,7,Fto become the island's fourth United
OL,8,FNations (UN) Junior Professional
OL,9,FOfficer.
OL,11,FLeila Osman will spend two years in
OL,12,FKyiv where she'll research the
OL,13,Fconflict and assess how best to spend
OL,14,FUN funds in the country to maximise
OL,15,Fits impact.
