OL,3,CJersey woman to spend two years in
OL,4,CUkraine as part of UN scheme
OL,6,FShe says: "When wars are going on all
OL,7,Fover the place and so many people need
OL,8,Fhelp, particularly in Ukraine,
OL,9,Falthough it's not so much in the news
OL,10,Fat the moment, it is so important to
OL,11,Fkeep funding going, so it's great that
OL,12,FI get to go at this point."
OL,14,FLeila added: "I feel very lucky as an
OL,15,Fislander to be taking part."
OL,17,FShe says: "To be able to aid displaced
OL,18,Fpeople in and around the war in
OL,19,FUkraine is an the opportunity that a
OL,20,Fyear ago I would never have imagined
OL,21,Fwould come my way.
