OL,3,CJersey woman to spend two years in
OL,4,CUkraine as part of UN scheme
OL,6,F"I'll have the chance to receive some
OL,7,Fgreat training and hopefully learn
OL,8,Ffrom people with bags of experience in
OL,9,Fthe field.
OL,11,F"As in any ongoing emergency, I'm
OL,12,Fexpecting that the learning curve will
OL,13,Fbe steep."
OL,15,FIt comes after Jersey Overseas Aid
OL,16,Fjoined the United Nations scheme in
OL,17,F2021, which allows young islanders to
OL,18,Fgo to different parts of the world to
OL,19,Fstart a career within the UN.
