OL,4,CUkraine as part of UN scheme
OL,6,FThe scheme has already seen two
OL,7,Fislanders employed within the
OL,8,Forganisation - both Faye Coggins and
OL,9,FJohnny Rebours took part in the scheme
OL,10,Fand now have roles in the United
OL,11,FNations.
OL,13,FFaye is working as an Executive
OL,14,FAssistant to the Bangladesh
OL,15,FRepresentative and Johnny as a Project
OL,16,FDevelopment and Reporting Officer with
OL,17,Fthe International Organisation for
OL,18,FMigration (IOM) in Beirut.
