OL,6,FMeanwhile, Rebecca Curtis is currently
OL,7,Fon the scheme and was deployed to
OL,8,FEgpyt.
OL,10,FLeila says Rebecca's advice was to
OL,11,F"keep a positive outlook and keep the
OL,12,Fresilience up, there will be
OL,13,Fchallenges, but it is important to
OL,14,Fkeep a positive outlook".
OL,16,FDeputy Carolyn Labey, the Minister for
OL,17,FInternational Development says: "This
OL,18,Fprogramme allows us to support
OL,19,FIslanders who want to establish a
OL,20,Fcareer in the humanitarian sector.
