OL,6,F"These dedicated individuals not only
OL,7,Fhelp some of the most vulnerable
OL,8,Fpeople in the world, and build their
OL,9,Fskills while doing so, they also serve
OL,10,Fas ambassadors for our caring, outward-
OL,11,Flooking Island on the global stage".
OL,13,FJersey Overseas Aid is currently
OL,14,Frecruiting a fifth islander to become
OL,15,Fa United Nations Junior Professional
OL,16,FOfficer.
OL,18,FThe chosen candidate will be based in
OL,19,FCox's Bazar in Bangladesh.
